rters_on_Aperture.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fianperegian.com%2FMy_FZ35_38_Webpage%2FEffect_of_Teleconverters_on_Aperture.html&d=cTAjkEOo76T5poMGkCYoadU7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=c8e9139f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://ianperegian.com/My_FZ35_38_Webpage/Effect_of_Teleconverters_on_Aperture.html</a><br />\n當然光線通過多幾塊鏡片，都會減少少通光，但唔多<br />\nbokeh唔識查<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  睇片唔覺有幾淺景深<br />\n<br />\n學識埋wide angle converter係會減光圈值<br />\n0.75x wide angle converter插F2鏡，會變F2.8 (2 / 0.75 ~= 2.8)<br />\n<br />\n唔講鏡片本身會增加咗幾多光學缺陷，當佢係完美鏡片<br />\n用嗰個咁嘅夾，要幾好運氣先可以完全對齊光軸係一直線"},{"pid":"6154af45c89e60508b9e11f825fde084b8805cf8","tid":963030,"uid":62204,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"98c68c89f6cd75c32d0170b0c32694f31d01d261","tid":963030,"uid":51137,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"542b42b7d1095c9655a0d9db8f4cb7d6b6652075","tid":963030,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T18:15:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>sensor咁細加個放大鏡真係會影響到景深?<br />\n60mm等效你話人像我冇意見 但你話係人像長焦我真係...???.jpg</blockquote>長焦與否都係比較而來 derrr <br />\n景深的確會多番少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>唔係咁計架清<br />\n你當佢2x teleconverter咁睇啦<br />\n即係2倍放大鏡<br />\n原本電話鏡頭當佢等效28mm，放大完就56mm (當佢差唔多60mm)<br />\n<br />\n呢啲teleconverter只係將已有嘅畫面放大，光圈孔徑係唔會變，原本個鏡頭屎眼幾大就幾大，唔會因為帶咗眼鏡你個屎眼會大咗<br />\n光圈<strong>值</strong>就會x2，即係由原本F2會變F4，會減咗兩級光，會由iso提高補償返<br />\n<br />\n唔會多咗bokeh，唔會淺景深過iphone tele</blockquote>會架清 <br />\nsensor size 都會影響景深<br />\nTele lens sensor 細啲 所以景深會冇咁明顯 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n感謝你詳盡既分析 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<strong>Tele lens sensor 細啲 所以景深會冇咁明顯</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/think.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-31T18:16:07.000Z","msg":"人地支lens有內置sensor"},"